Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.50,0:15:21.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,出發
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.58,0:16:00.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gaia? 竟然還有那種東西
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.58,0:16:02.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到底是什麼樣的組織
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.14,0:16:09.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,距離小艇的發射地點還有多遠
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.64,0:16:12.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還剩20 不 是25
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.56,0:16:15.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請努力堅持到那裏
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.52,0:16:16.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.28,0:16:22.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.00,0:16:34.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉克絲 一定要趕上
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.14,0:16:55.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.35,0:16:59.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Strike
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.95,0:17:17.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,基拉
