Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.93,0:17:22.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,基拉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.09,0:17:23.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.43,0:17:26.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 但是我擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.77,0:17:54.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,傻瓜 那就快進Eternal
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.86,0:17:57.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去拿你的機體
