Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.26,0:18:22.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉克絲
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.98,0:18:32.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,基拉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.15,0:18:33.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉克絲
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.28,0:18:37.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.78,0:18:38.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,基拉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.24,0:18:42.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看到你平安
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.87,0:18:45.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的很高興
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.83,0:18:47.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也是 基拉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.46,0:18:53.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.09,0:18:56.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.51,0:19:01.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,隊長
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.93,0:19:06.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉克絲 趕快
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.10,0:19:07.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.00,0:19:29.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.12,0:19:34.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣我又能好好地戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.34,0:19:36.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.00,0:19:37.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,基拉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.01,0:19:41.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等著我 馬上就回來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.89,0:19:45.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後回去吧 回大家那裏
